research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Brookshire, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which is a mayor-council system. Robert Richards was elected Mayor in the May 3, 2025, city elections. Eric Green serves as Mayor Pro Tem and holds Council Member Position 5. Monique Taylor is the Council Member for Position 1, Lyndon Stamps for Position 2, and Eileen McDade for Position 4. Council Member Position 3 is currently vacant.
